{"text_id":169858,"tokens":["The"," use"," of"," driver","less"," cars"," has"," emerged"," as"," an"," intriguing"," innovation"," with"," a"," myriad"," of"," potential"," benefits"," and"," drawbacks","."," On"," the"," one"," hand",","," driver","less"," cars"," have"," the"," capacity"," to"," significantly"," reduce"," fuel"," consumption",","," as"," they"," can"," communicate"," with"," one"," another"," and"," travel"," at"," optimized"," speeds",","," leading"," to"," decreased"," traffic"," and"," less"," stop","-","and","-","go"," driving","."," This"," could"," have"," a"," positive"," impact"," on"," the"," environment"," and"," reduce"," our"," reliance"," on"," fossil"," fuels","."," ","\n","Additionally",","," driver","less"," cars"," could"," offer"," more"," flexibility"," in"," public"," transportation",","," as"," they"," can"," be"," programmed"," to"," operate"," on"," a"," set"," route"," and"," schedule",","," picking"," up"," passengers"," as"," needed","."," This"," could"," improve"," accessibility"," and"," affordability"," of"," transportation"," for"," many"," people","."," ","\n","However",","," there"," are"," also"," several"," concerns"," associated"," with"," driver","less"," cars","."," One"," of"," the"," main"," risks"," is"," the"," potential"," for"," human"," error"," in"," the"," technology"," itself","."," Even"," with"," sophisticated"," sensors"," and"," algorithms",","," there"," is"," still"," a"," chance"," for"," driver","less"," cars"," to"," make"," mistakes"," or"," encounter"," situations"," they"," cannot"," handle",","," which"," could"," result"," in"," accidents"," and"," harm"," to"," passengers"," or"," others"," on"," the"," road","."," ","\n","Another"," issue"," is"," the"," need"," for"," constant"," attention"," and"," monitoring"," of"," the"," vehicle","'","s"," performance",","," even"," when"," the"," car"," is"," driving"," itself","."," If"," a"," passenger"," or"," operator"," becomes"," distrac